---
layout: base
title: "Blog"
description: "Escrevo para organizar ideias, questionar práticas comuns da web e compartilhar aprendizados sobre
acessibilidade, front-end e pensamento crítico."
permalink: "/blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 12
---
<div>
  <h1 class="mb-6 p-name font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-3xl">Blog</h1>
  <p class="mb-4">{{ description }}</p>
  <a class="hidden u-url" href="{{ site.url }}/blog/"></a>

  <ol class="space-y-8 h-feed">
    {% for post in pagination.items %}
    <li class="py-6 border-brand-gray-500 border-b h-entry">
      <h2 class="p-name font-bold text-2xl">
        <a class="text-brand-red-500 hover:text-brand-red-600 text-xl underline u-url" href="{{ post.url }}">{{
          post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      <time class="text-sm dt-published" datetime="{{ post.data.pubDate | toISOString }}">
        Publicado em: {{ post.data.pubDate | readableDate }}
      </time>
      <div class="mt-2 p-summary">
        {{ post.data.description or (post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(160)) }}
      </div>
      <div class="space-x-2 mt-2 text-sm">
        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
        <a class="bg-brand-gray-200 p-category px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold text-brand-dark-500"
          href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/">#{{ tag }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</div>

{% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
{% include 'components/pagination.njk' %}
{% endif %}